sql_statement.static: SELECT P.Name AS `Port Name`,(SELECT ifnull(SUM(TX.FrameCount),0) FROM TxEotStreamResults AS TX WHERE TX.RxPortName=P.NAME)-(SELECT ifnull(SUM(RX.SigFrameCount),0) FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RX WHERE RX.PortName=P.NAME AND RX.IsExpectedPort=1)+(SELECT ifnull(SUM(RX.DuplicateFrameCount),0) FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RX WHERE RX.PortName=P.Name) AS `Rx Signature Packets Lost`,(SELECT ifnull(SUM(RX.SigFrameCount),0) FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RX WHERE RX.PortName=P.Name AND RX.IsExpectedPort=0) AS `Rx Misdirected Packets`,(SELECT ifnull(SUM(RX.DuplicateFrameCount),0) FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RX WHERE RX.PortName=P.Name) AS `Rx Duplicate Packets`,(SELECT ifnull(SUM(RX.SigFrameCount),0) FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RX WHERE RX.PortName=P.Name AND RX.IsExpectedPort=1) AS `Rx Signature Packets`,(SELECT ifnull(SUM(TX.FrameCount),0) FROM TxEotStreamResults AS TX WHERE TX.PortName=P.Name) AS `Tx Signature Packets` FROM Port AS P

CREATE TABLE vSwitchIPPLatency_IncompleteBurst AS SELECT prt.Handle AS Handle, prt.Location AS Location, gen2.GeneratorSigFrameCount AS TxFrameCount FROM Port AS prt INNER JOIN GeneratorPortResults AS gen2 ON prt.Handle=gen2.ParentPort AND prt.Handle IN (SELECT gen.ParentPort AS Handle FROM GeneratorPortResults AS gen INNER JOIN StreamBlock AS sb ON gen.ParentPort=sb.ParentHnd AND gen.GeneratorSigFrameCount != (SELECT NumberOfFlows FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_NumberOfFlows))

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE vSwitchIPPLatency_ExpectedStreamResults AS SELECT  tx.StreamId AS StreamId, (SELECT Location FROM Port WHERE Handle=RxPort) AS RxPort, tx.FrameCount AS TxFrames, rx.FrameCount AS RxFrames, DroppedFrameCount AS DroppedFrameCount, DuplicateFrameCount AS DuplicateFrameCount, MinLatency AS MinLatency, MaxLatency AS MaxLatency, TotalLatency AS TotalLatency, AvgLatency AS AvgLatency FROM TxEotStreamResults AS tx INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS rx ON tx.StreamId=rx.Comp32 AND rx.IsExpectedPort='1'

INSERT INTO vSwitchIPPLatency_ExpectedStreamResults (StreamId,RxPort,TxFrames,RxFrames,DroppedFrameCount,DuplicateFrameCount,MinLatency,MaxLatency,TotalLatency,AvgLatency) SELECT tx.StreamId, RxPort, tx.FrameCount, 0, tx.FrameCount, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL FROM TxEotStreamResults AS tx WHERE StreamId NOT IN (SELECT Comp32 FROM RxEotStreamResults)
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS vSwitchIPPLatency_TempExpectedStreamResults
SELECT * FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_ExpectedStreamResults

CREATE TABLE vSwitchIPPLatency_StrayFramesReceived AS SELECT  tx.StreamId AS StreamId, RxPort AS RxPort, tx.FrameCount AS TxFrames, rx.FrameCount AS RxFrames, DroppedFrameCount, DuplicateFrameCount, MinLatency AS MinLatency, MaxLatency AS MaxLatency, TotalLatency AS TotalLatency, AvgLatency AS AvgLatency FROM TxEotStreamResults AS tx INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS rx ON tx.StreamId=rx.Comp32 AND rx.IsExpectedPort='0'

sql_statement.static: UPDATE vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter SET NumberOfFlows=(SELECT NumberOfFlows FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter)
UPDATE vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter SET TxFrameCount=(SELECT Sum(TxFrames) FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_ExpectedStreamResults)
UPDATE vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter SET RxFrameCount=(SELECT Sum(RxFrames - DuplicateFrameCount) FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_ExpectedStreamResults)
UPDATE vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter SET DroppedFrameCount=(SELECT TxFrameCount - RxFrameCount FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter)
UPDATE vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter SET DuplicateFrameCount=(SELECT DuplicateFrameCount FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_ExpectedStreamResults)
UPDATE vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter SET MinLatency=(SELECT ROUND(MIN(MinLatency),3) FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_ExpectedStreamResults)
UPDATE vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter SET MaxLatency=(SELECT ROUND(MAX(MaxLatency),3) FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_ExpectedStreamResults)
UPDATE vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter SET AvgLatency=(SELECT ROUND(AVG(AvgLatency),3) FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_ExpectedStreamResults WHERE RxFrames > 0)
SELECT * FROM vSwitchIPPLatency_CurrIter
